message.body: Hi Ingrid! I just logged onto my FB which has been deactivated for a really long time and I saw that you got engaged!!! congrats hon!! I'm so excited for you! ❤️❤️❤️
Yayayayay!! I want to visit you soon for lunch or something fun!
I should be in Baltimore for June or July because I'm housesitting, so let's hang out a lot then! I miss you!
I miss you too girl! yes let me know when you are here, we'll def get together. can't wait! see ya!
